<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men bù shì yīng xióng wǒ men shì zhǔ de bīng yī èr sān sì wǔ liù qī yīng shí qù chū zhēng
 wǒ men bù shì yīng xióng wǒ men shì zhǔ de bīng liǎng jiān shuāng huā fēng yǔ jiān chéng yǒng gǎn xiàng qián chōng
 yíng zhe fēng xuě, tà zhe ní nìng zhǔ fā mìng lìng pīn mìng gǎn sǐ wán chéng dà shǐ mìng.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men shì zhǔ de bīng 迦南247</title>
